Forza Vinyl Studio third-party notice

Kloudy's FH6 Painter bundles a modified Windows build of Forza Vinyl Studio as
an offline FH6 JSON editor.

Original project:
https://github.com/willn05/forza-vinyl-studio

Original project credits from upstream documentation:
- willn05: original Forza Vinyl Studio project.
- A-Dawg#0001: original Forza Painter dependency credited by upstream.
- D3FEKT#1337: Modelbin template script credited by upstream.

Kloudy's FH6 Painter modifications:
- FH6 JSON load/export path.
- Full FH6 shape library wiring used by the editor.
- Shape popout/sidebar, favorites, overlay image, project save/load, autosave,
  undo/redo, duplicate, and FH-style move/scale/stretch/rotate controls.
- Bundled self-contained Windows runtime for launcher use.

